text: Roshni Khatri () (born February 19, 1996 in Lalitpur, Nepal) is a Nepalese model, celebrity & beauty pageant winner of Miss Nepal Earth 2016. She has also represented Nepal in Miss Earth 2016. == References == Category:1996 births Category:Nepalese beauty pageant winners Category:Living people Category:Nepalese models
